.ps-section--vendor.ps-vendor-best-fees
    .container
        .ps-section__header
            p BEST FEES TO START
            h4 Affordable, transparent, and secure
        .ps-section__content
            h5 It doesn’t cost a thing to list up to 50 items a month, and you only pay after your stuff sells. It’s just a small percent of the money you earn
            .ps-section__numbers
                figure
                    h3 $0
                    span List Fee
                figure
                    h3 5%
                    span Final Value Fee
            .ps-section__desc
                figure
                    figcaption Here's what you get for your fee:
                    ul
                        li A worldwide community of more than 160 million shoppers.
                        li Shipping labels you can print at home, with big discounts on postage.
                        li Seller protection and customer support to help you sell your stuff.
            .ps-section__highlight
                img(src="img/icons/vendor-4.png" alt="")
                figure
                    p We process payments with PayPal, an external payments platform that allows you to process transactions with a variety of payment methods. Funds from PayPal sales on Martfury will be deposited into your PayPal account.
            .ps-section__footer
                p Listing fees are billed for 0.20 USD, so if your bank’s currency is not USD, the amount in your currency may vary based on changes in the exchange rate.
